'''瑙堡'''（{{Lang-prs|قلعه نو}} ）是[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[巴德吉斯省|巴德吉斯省]]瑙堡区西北部的省府。2006年，当地人口估计有九千人，其中八成是[[塔吉克族|塔吉克人]]、[[哈扎拉人|哈扎拉人]]和艾玛克哈扎拉人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.world-gazetteer.com/wg.php?x=1138085326&men=gpro&lng=en&dat=32&geo=449988312&srt=npan&col=ohdq |title=World Gazetteer: Qalʿeh-ye Naw - profile of geographical entity including name variants |access-date=2021-08-25 |archive-date=2007-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001090801/http://www.world-gazetteer.com/wg.php?x=1138085326&men=gpro&lng=en&dat=32&geo=449988312&srt=npan&col=ohdq |dead-url=yes }}</ref>其他种族有[[普什圖人|普什图人]]、[[俾路支人|俾路支人]]和[[乌孜别克族|乌兹别克人]]。

2015年统计数据显示，瑙堡人口有64,125人<ref>{{Cite web|title=The State of Afghan Cities Report 2015|url=http://unhabitat.org/books/soac2015/|access-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031111515/http://unhabitat.org/books/soac2015/|archive-date=2015-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>、6个警区，总面积3,752公顷<ref name="#2">{{Cite web|title=The State of Afghan Cities Report 2015|url=http://unhabitat.org/books/soac2015_volume2/|access-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031111658/http://unhabitat.org/books/soac2015_volume2/|archive-date=2015-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当地建有7,125套住宅<ref name="#2"/>。

瑙堡是位于阿富汗西部的省级中心。荒地占总面积的49%<ref name="#2"/> ，仅有28%已建成<ref name="#2"/>。而建成用地中有60%为住宅用地。 <ref name="#2"/>由于机场位于第4区，因此该地有大量的机构与交通用地。 <ref name="#2"/>

它有一个小机场—— [[瑙堡机场|瑙堡机场]]。

2021年7月7日，[[塔利班|塔利班]]开始袭击该镇<ref name="bbc">{{Cite news|date=2021-07-07|title=Taliban battle their way into western Afghan city|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-57748695|work=|location=BBC News|accessdate=2021-07-07|archive-date=2021-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210817002705/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-57748695|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，但被[[阿富汗军队|政府军]]击溃。战争造成69名塔利班士兵阵亡，23人受伤<ref>{{Cite news|title=69 Taliban terrorists killed, 23 injured as Afghan forces regain control of Qala-e-Naw city - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/69-taliban-terrorists-killed-23-injured-as-afghan-forces-regain-control-of-qala-e-naw-city/articleshow/84228756.cms|accessdate=2021-07-09|work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|date=2021-07-08|language=en|archive-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813092631/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/69-taliban-terrorists-killed-23-injured-as-afghan-forces-regain-control-of-qala-e-naw-city/articleshow/84228756.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该市在2021年8月12日被塔利班夺取（约与[[赫拉特|赫拉特]]沦陷日相同，作为[[2021年塔利班攻勢|2021年塔利班攻势]]的一部分）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-58184202 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-08-25 |archive-date=2021-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812192131/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-58184202 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Afghanistan Collapse Accelerates as 2 Vital Cities Near Fall to Taliban|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/08/12/world/asia/kandahar-afghanistan-taliban.html|access-date=2021-08-12|author=Sharif|first=Hussein|work=Nytimes|publisher=New York Times|archive-date=2021-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812174047/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/08/12/world/asia/kandahar-afghanistan-taliban.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此地为塔利班夺取的第十三个省会。

